Only admin and user roles can call this service.<br>
Root is considered as an admin of his company.<br>
For each caller, this service returns all collections of his company. If there is no result, an empty list is
returned.<br>]]>
        </wadl:doc>
        <wadl:response>
          <wadl:doc>
            <![CDATA[collections of caller's company]]>
          </wadl:doc>
          <wadl:representation mediaType="text/xml"/>
